snippet.title: Crash Bandicoot Nitro Kart 3D (Zeebo Gameplay) | Forgotten Games
snippet.description:
Gameplay of the Zeebo version of the game Crash Bandicoot Nitro Kart 3D, released only in Brazil and Mexico in 2009. Played on the newly released Zeebo emulator Infuse by Tuxality (http://tuxality.net/projects/infuse_zeebo_emulator).
Support the channel: https://ko-fi.com/neogamer
https://www.patreon.com/neogamertvga
